title: Greenhouse, Berber carpet and vinyl plank flooring
posting_body: ['Live where ideas and interests ignite', 'Be among the first to live in The Spring District in Bellevue, Washington.', 'We are creating a neighborhood that draws people in, sparks both business and personal passions weaving an intellectual tapestry that drives new ideas.', 'Sparc Apartments is the catalyst welcoming you to a new living experience where urban meets suburban.', 'Lease studios, one, two and three bedroom apartments.', 'Not to mention innovative Townhomes and Live work lofts.', 'Live minutes from Downtown Bellevue, Kirkland, Redmond with easy access to I-405 and the Microsoft Campus.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 21', 'OR Text', '21', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 537 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Berber carpet and vinyl plank flooring', '- Full size, stacked washer and dryer', '- Patios and balconies in select homes', '- Electric or gas range', '- Custom pendant lights in kitchen', '- Stainless or black Whirlpool appliances', '- Floor-to-ceiling windows in select homes', '- Quartz countertops in kitchen and bathrooms', 'Community Amenities', '- Catering kitchen', '- Greenhouse', '- Mini putting green', '- Public courtyard', '- Bicycle storage & repair station', '- Raised garden beds', '- Event space', '- Pet washing station', '- Rooftop deck', '- Well-stocked fitness center', '- Wi-Fi Lounge', '- Games & TV lounge', '- 4,500 SF outdoor playground', '- Early childhood education center', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sparc at Spring District', '1201 121st Avenue NE, Bellevue, WA, 98005', 'QzNo7sp4sy']
